---
title: Kiwi-Spiced Lamb Meatballs with Charred Broccoli Salad & Mayonnaise
description: These lamb meatballs have been mixed with our new favourite - Kiwi spice blend! Smokey flavours in tender lamb mince are the
perfect complement to charred broccoli in a sweet and zingy dressing. Dig in!

